  "prompt": "Where can I get an activation code for the online game, Clash of Kings?",
  "response": "To get an activation code for the online game **Clash of Kings**, you can try the following methods:\n\n1. **Official Game Events**:  \n   Participate in official in-game events, promotions, or giveaways hosted by the developers (**Elex**). These often reward players with activation codes or other bonuses.\n\n2. **Social Media Channels**:  \n   Follow the official **Clash of Kings** social media accounts (Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, etc.). Developers frequently share codes during special events or updates.\n\n3. **Partner Websites**:  \n   Check gaming websites or forums that collaborate with **Clash of Kings**. Sometimes, they provide exclusive codes as part of promotions.\n\n4. **Streamers and Influencers**:  \n   Watch **Clash of Kings** streamers or influencers on platforms like YouTube or Twitch. They may share codes with their audience during live streams or videos.\n\n5. **In-Game Purchases**:  \n   Some activation codes or rewards are bundled with in-game purchases or special offers in the store.\n\n6. **Customer Support**:  \n   Reach out to the game\u2019s customer support team and inquire about any ongoing promotions or codes.\n\nMake sure to verify the source of the code to avoid scams or fraudulent websites. Always use official channels to ensure the authenticity of the code.",
